---
title: Creamy Beef, Bacon & Basil Pesto Fusilli with Baby Leaves & Parmesan
description: Let’s whip up a dinner filled with everyone’s favourites: bacon, beef, cheese and basil pesto. Toss them through perfectly al dent fusilli
and sprinkle on sharp Parmesan to elevate this dish to superstar level. Sit back, and enjoy!
